"tid":686094,"uid":33868,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T06:23:08.000Z","msg":"中華民國<br />\n台灣省、福建省<br />\n6直轄市"},{"pid":"03544fbbff324ae1ad425f79604872e65946a406","tid":686094,"uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e89342e540d8ec7ea08a19360be9e6f3e981f9eb","tid":686094,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":8,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"5f160f5209956cb71bdb958cb6ff7a035a85d914","tid":686094,"uid":170159,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"133677dfbb54a7c62c755c9a08e50a2fc7426ff6","tid":686094,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T06:04:49.000Z","msg":"所以咪係, 蔡英文政府都用「台灣省」囉<br />\n<br />\n即係自作業囉"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T06:18:20.000Z","msg":"on9<br />\n呢個明顯講緊中華民國臺灣省<br />\n唔撚係所謂嘅「中華人民共和國臺灣省」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T06:19:41.000Z","msg":"即係「台灣省」<br />\n<br />\n你蔡英文唔用「台灣省」三隻字, 咪唔會被人騎劫囉"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T06:23:37.000Z","msg":"你係講緊台獨(修改中華民國憲法，將台灣由中華民國統治下脫離)?<br />\n地理上、法制上，中華民國同台灣係有些少分別"},{"pid":"ea29e84a212f9165e193aa5d74f987fb8899db22","tid":686094,"uid":180035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"35f4b29dcaf98f5e4c50ce64259226ed6737c172","tid":686094,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T05:52:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>《蘋果》翻查近年改版或訂正的小學常識課本，當中不少改動均含政治色彩，包括在辛亥革命部分刪去「中華民國」字眼，更稱台灣為「台灣省」。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n周杰倫部車：<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://s2.buzzhand.net/uploads/10/d/1015810/15073342208447.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs2.buzzhand.net%2Fuploads%2F10%2Fd%2F1015810%2F15073342208447.jpg&h=1309f30b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁要問蔡英文點解自己用「台灣省」啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T06:24:12.000Z","msg":"台灣的車輛號牌經過多次改制。在未實施精省政策之前，車牌上的&ldquo;台灣省&rdquo;字樣一直存在。 <br />\n<br />\n　　那麼，何謂&ldquo;精省&rdquo;呢？李登輝執政時，決定廢除台灣省&ldquo;自治地位&rdquo;，並於1998年通過了將省虛級化（精省）的方案，將省政府改為&ldquo;行政院&rdquo;的派出機關，移除省政府原有的地方自治功能。目前，台灣省政府只是一個象徵性的機構，不具備實施地方自治的能力。 <br />\n<br />\n　　台灣社會政治架構的變動直接影響了台灣車牌的編碼模式。從2007年開始，台灣當局因應精省等政策，將車牌內容取消上方用漢字標示的&ldquo;台灣省&rdquo;、&ldquo;台北市&rdquo;、&ldquo;高雄市&rdquo;、&ldquo;金門縣&rdquo;、&ldquo;連江縣&rdquo;等地域識別，2008年起，原本放置該識別的地方以英文字母取代。 <br />\n<br />\n　　目前，台灣車輛在精省政策前後印製的新老車牌都有使用，便造成有的車輛上標明&ldquo;台灣省&rdquo;字樣，有的卻沒有該字樣的情況。而&ldquo;台灣省&rdquo;三個字的運用以及刪去是否反映出台灣社會的某種心態，便是仁者見仁的問題。 <br />\n<br />\n　　不過無可否認的是，這小小的車牌背後竟然折射的是整個兩岸關係變遷的歷史，濃縮著台灣民眾對中國及對台灣認識的變動，值得去品味和深思。"},{"pid":"f9810148d07feee6f1f5354d6b89697e7751c3ef","tid":686094,"uid":52595,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T06:27:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cedce6c550251426e46ef3ab9582bc0f5807c842","tid":686094,"uid":51183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T07:45:30.000Z","msg":"台灣省已經於1997年起凍結<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aabdd7f3cd3e9e936478c62f0381fcce1354d6d7","tid":686094,"uid":39470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-01T17:44:23.000Z","msg":"成功爭取金門馬祖獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0064efe79c826b3eeb940649776783dabe107119","tid":686094,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"reply